    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "YoungPileUp[shape] returns a list of Young shapes resulting from adding \
a new cell to shape. YoungPileUp[shape, d] restricts that the new shapes have \
at most d rows. YoungPileUp[syt] returns a list of standard Young tableaux \
resulting from adding a new cell numbered n + 1 to the standard Young tableau \
syt of degree n. YoungPileUp[syt, d] restricts that thew standard Young \
tableaux have at most d rows. YoungPileUp[gyp] and YoungPileUp[gyp, d] are \
equivalent to YoungPileUp[syt] and YoungPileUp[syt, d] with Gelfand-Young \
pattern gyp corresponding to standard Young tableau syt. They returns \
Gelfand-Young patterns, the equivalents of standard Young tableaux.", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "YoungPileUp", 
